('openrouter:qwen/qwen2.5-vl-72b-instruct:free', 'Qwen: Qwen2.5 VL 72B Instruct (free)', 'openrouter', 'OpenRouter', 'qwen/qwen2.5-vl-72b-instruct:free', 32768, null, true, true, false, ARRAY['chat', 'vision'], 'Qwen2.5-VL is proficient in recognizing common objects such as flowers, birds, fish, and insects. It is also highly capable of analyzing texts, charts, icons, graphics, and layouts within images.', 42),
('openrouter:mistralai/mistral-small-24b-instruct-2501:free', 'Mistral: Mistral Small 3 (free)', 'openrouter', 'OpenRouter', 'mistralai/mistral-small-24b-instruct-2501:free', 32768, null, true, true, false, ARRAY['chat'], 'Mistral Small 3 is a 24B-parameter language model optimized for low-latency performance across common AI tasks. Released under the Apache 2.0 license, it features both pre-trained and instruction-tuned versions designed for efficient local deployment.

