('openrouter:deepseek/deepseek-r1-distill-qwen-14b:free', 'DeepSeek: R1 Distill Qwen 14B (free)', 'openrouter', 'OpenRouter', 'deepseek/deepseek-r1-distill-qwen-14b:free', 64000, null, true, true, false, ARRAY['chat', 'reasoning'], 'DeepSeek R1 Distill Qwen 14B is a distilled large language model based on [Qwen 2.5 14B](https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-R1-Distill-Qwen-14B), using outputs from [DeepSeek R1](/deepseek/deepseek-r1). It outperforms OpenAI''s o1-mini across various benchmarks, achieving new state-of-the-art results for dense models.

