('openrouter:deepseek/deepseek-r1-distill-llama-70b:free', 'DeepSeek: R1 Distill Llama 70B (free)', 'openrouter', 'OpenRouter', 'deepseek/deepseek-r1-distill-llama-70b:free', 8192, 4096, true, true, false, ARRAY['chat', 'reasoning'], 'DeepSeek R1 Distill Llama 70B is a distilled large language model based on [Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct](/meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct), using outputs from [DeepSeek R1](/deepseek/deepseek-r1). The model combines advanced distillation techniques to achieve high performance across multiple benchmarks, including:

