('openrouter:qwen/qwen-2.5-coder-32b-instruct:free', 'Qwen2.5 Coder 32B Instruct (free)', 'openrouter', 'OpenRouter', 'qwen/qwen-2.5-coder-32b-instruct:free', 32768, null, true, true, false, ARRAY['chat'], 'Qwen2.5-Coder is the latest series of Code-Specific Qwen large language models (formerly known as CodeQwen). Qwen2.5-Coder brings the following improvements upon CodeQwen1.5:

