('openrouter:meta-llama/llama-3.2-11b-vision-instruct:free', 'Meta: Llama 3.2 11B Vision Instruct (free)', 'openrouter', 'OpenRouter', 'meta-llama/llama-3.2-11b-vision-instruct:free', 131072, 2048, true, true, false, ARRAY['chat', 'vision'], 'Llama 3.2 11B Vision is a multimodal model with 11 billion parameters, designed to handle tasks combining visual and textual data. It excels in tasks such as image captioning and visual question answering, bridging the gap between language generation and visual reasoning. Pre-trained on a massive dataset of image-text pairs, it performs well in complex, high-accuracy image analysis.

